            "value": "Trust %@@%@:%lld for %@?\n\nFingerprint:\n%@\n\nCompare with this on the Mac:\nssh-keygen -E sha256 -lf /etc/ssh/ssh_host_*.pub\n\nContinue only if one SHA256 fingerprint matches exactly."
